1. Main nearest kya dhoond raha hu?
   (greater/smaller)

2. Kya kuch candidates future me useless ho sakte hain?

3. Useless candidate ki condition kya hai?

4. Mujhe order maintain karna hai?
   (increasing/decreasing)

5. Stack use hoga ya Queue?